===Format===
* '''Open Qualifiers:''' ''
** Total scores of the squad in 2 matches will be considered
** {{bgcolortext|up|''Top 112 teams ''}} qualify for the ''Challenger Round''.

* '''Challenger Round:'''
** Top 112 teams + 16 Invited Teams
** Teams will be divided into 8 groups
** 6 Matches per group
** {{bgcolortext|up|''Top 7 teams ''}} from each group  qualify for the ''Contender Round''.

* '''Contender Round:'''
** Top 56 teams + 8 Invited Teams
** Teams will be divided into 4 groups
** 9 Matches per group
** {{bgcolortext|up|''Top 6 teams ''}} from each group  qualify for the ''League Stage''.

* '''League Round:'''
** Top 24 teams + 8 Invited Teams
** Teams will be divided into 4 groups
** Top 24 will qualify to Finals of each week
**  {{bgcolortext|up|''Top 24'' }} teams based on the cumulative point standings of the finals of each week will qualify for ''Quarter Finals''.

* '''Quarter Finals:'''
** Teams will be divided into 3 groups
** Round Robin Format 3 days in a week
** Bottom 4 teams will be eliminated
** Top 24 will qualify to Finals of each week
**  {{bgcolortext|up|''Top 20''}} teams  will qualify for ''Semi Finals''.

* '''Semi Finals:'''
** Teams will be divided into 5 groups
** Round Robin Format 4 days in a week
** Bottom 4 teams will be eliminated
** Top 24 will qualify to Finals of each week
**  {{bgcolortext|up|''Top 16''}} teams  will qualify for ''Grand Finals''.

* '''Grand Finals:''' ''July 13th - 17th, 2022
** Squad {{Abbr/TPP}}, Top 16 teams of ''Semi Finals''.
** 30 matches total, over span of 5 days.
